{
  "title": "Xenial Malty Turkish Mincemeat Kazandibi",
  "description": "A malty and cozy Turkish dish featuring mincemeat, reduced to a paleo-friendly dessert, formed into a kazandibi.",
  "cuisine": "Turkish",
